original_title: Sri Lanka, Maldives presidents in bilateral discussions
original_body_lines: ECONOMYNEXT – President Ranil Wickremesinghe met the President of the Republic of Maldives Dr Mohamed Muizzu in Malé, Maldives on Friday.
“President Wickremesinghe and Maldivian president Dr Muizzu engaged in bilateral discussions,” the president’s media division announced on X (twitter).
Wickremesinghe, who was present at the inauguration ceremony marking the commencement of his presidency earlier in the day, congratulated Dr Muizzu.
He also had a meeting with the US Agency for International Development (USAID)  Administrator  Samantha Power, in the capital city of Malé, following the swearing-in ceremony of Dr Muizzu.
